    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just... it's not even just the sadness. it's the emptiness. i look at his bowl and his bed and it just feels like a giant hole in my chest. it's like i'm just going through the motions of living but there's nothing actually there. it feels like there's no reason to keep trying to fill the space when the person who made it special is gone. i'm just so tired of the ache. it never stops.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
