      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what if i don't want to \"carry\" it? carrying it feels like being crushed every single day. you talk about integrating it like it's some beautiful thing, but it just feels like a debt i'm paying for something i didn't even want. i'm just so done with the struggle. i look at how quiet everything is and i just think... wouldn't it be easier if everything just stopped? if the noise and the ache and the emptiness just went away forever?",
